{"tid":1508313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾個做海關入境既舊同學，最近都係到幸災樂禍","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T12:04:15.000Z","uid":214534,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7347e9433f25bbadb4256048a305b5d7b86ac4","tid":1508313,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"圈子入邊總共有三個舊同學做緊紀律部隊，兩個海關一個入境，<br />\n平時佢地都係同學group到呻，好慘又攰上司又乜又乜，<br />\n但係呢排成日係group到尻噏，話好彩當初冇貪嗰2000幾蚊既起薪去做警犬，<br />\n唔係一定辛苦到仆街，吃力不討好，係到用埋啲恥笑sticker<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為毒撚好少覆既我都忍唔住和應佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個話用返佔中計，黑警起碼要用返幾年洗底，媾女方面又少左堆人爭"},{"pid":"5288eabf59f38da5d4cf99dd3749356b7484df94","tid":1508313,"uid":2994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"消防都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f62eaef7e4337addcb370e97de6d1927d81558","tid":1508313,"uid":52090,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個真，當D做狗笑人地人工低兩千幾<br />\n今日成班同學會，冇人請狗去，<br />\n個個都屌鳩隻狗<br />\n入境同學由心笑出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29abc9dfc45e12383a09f05be6689ed393954289","tid":1508313,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:15:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！</span></span>(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-aut